         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">538.7002-9</ph> Tribally controlled schools.  </title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p rev="Change 178 March 25, 2024" class="- topic/p ">25 U.S.C. 2507(a)(6) allows tribally controlled schools, as defined under 25 U.S.C. 2511, that have an active grant pursuant to 25 U.S.C. chapter 27 to purchase supplies or services for the purposes of carrying out the grant. </p>
